4?t=1766168603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a massive technology tree, discovering new structures and materials as your factory’s power expands. Use ancient technology scattered throughout the world to upgrade Otto’s mainframe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960480/extras/ee334ebdf30e7838d5f7b6024e2d5946.poster.avif?t=1766168603\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960480/extras/ee334ebdf30e7838d5f7b6024e2d5946.webm?t=1766168603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1960480/extras/ee334ebdf30e7838d5f7b6024e2d5946.mp4?t=1766168603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious auto-defense system has awakened to protect the world’s resources – from you! Defeat the drones with a sword, blaster, and an auto-defense system of your own.</p>",
